This paper is primarily focused on the expressive power of higher-order Datalog in the context of databases, which suggests that cs.DB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves complexity theory and logic, which are covered by cs.LO and cs.CC. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential practical applications of higher-order Datalog, which could fall under cs.AI and cs.DS.
